<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM2.7">
<l>pēta naṉkaṟi vārka ḷōṭivai pēci ṉāṟperi tiṉcuvai</l>
<l>yātu moṉṟaṟi yāta piḷḷaika ḷōmai nīnalin teṉpayaṉ</l>
<l>ōta mākaṭal vaṇṇā vuṉmaṇa vāṭṭi māroṭu cūḻaṟum</l>
<l>cētu pantan tiruttiṉā yeṅkaḷ ciṟṟil vantu citaiyēlē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [You] say these things to people who understand the nuances well,</l>
<l rend="indent">it would be greatly, sweetly tasteful.</l>
<l>What is the use of causing distress to us girls who do not know anything?</l>
<l>O You of the hue of the vast ocean [full] of waves!</l>
<l>An oath on Your wives is [now] decided! O You who made a bridge properly!</l>
<l>Do not come and trample down our small [sand] house!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
